    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Tao</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg/330px-Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg/500px-Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg/960px-Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taoism\">Taoist</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taijitu\">Taijitu</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Tao</b>,<br />\na <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and later <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> compliant chess engine by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, famous for its attacking playing style encouraged by an <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> cooked by <a href=\"/Cock_de_Gorter\" title=\"Cock de Gorter\">Cock de Gorter</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. Tao played the <a href=\"/WMCCC_2001\" title=\"WMCCC 2001\">WMCCC 2001</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maastricht\">Maastricht</a>, six <a href=\"/Dutch_Open_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"Dutch Open Computer Chess Championship\">Dutch Open Computer Chess Championships</a> and four <a href=\"/International_CSVN_Tournament\" title=\"International CSVN Tournament\">International CSVN Tournaments</a> from <a href=\"/DOCCC_2000\" title=\"DOCCC 2000\">2000</a> until <a href=\"/DOCCC_2005\" title=\"DOCCC 2005\">2005</a>, and three <a href=\"/CCT_Tournaments\" title=\"CCT Tournaments\">CCT Tournaments</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Photos_.26_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos &amp; Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Description\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Tao is a <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> engine that uses <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a> without root <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">aspiration windows</a>. Tao applies <a href=\"/Incremental_Updates\" title=\"Incremental Updates\">incremental updated</a> <a href=\"/Attack_and_Defend_Maps\" title=\"Attack and Defend Maps\">attacks</a>, incremental <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">move generation</a>, uses <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE</a> to prune losing <a href=\"/Captures\" title=\"Captures\">captures</a>, and <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extends</a>  <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">checks</a>, <a href=\"/One_Reply_Extensions\" title=\"One Reply Extensions\">one reply</a>, <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">recaptures</a> and <a href=\"/Mate_Threat_Extensions\" title=\"Mate Threat Extensions\">mate threats</a> along with <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">null move pruning</a> of <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">R=2</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nIt further considers <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">check</a> giving moves in <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">quiescence search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. Version 5.5 uses <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">tuning</a> based on <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">temporal differences</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos_.26_Games\">Photos &amp; Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Photos &amp; Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Hamstra32.jpg\" src=\"/images/4/40/Hamstra32.jpg\" width=\"560\" height=\"412\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/DOCCC_2004\" title=\"DOCCC 2004\">DOCCC 2004</a>: <a href=\"/Elke_Van_Vlierberghe\" title=\"Elke Van Vlierberghe\">Elke Van Vlierberghe</a> and <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tao</a> - <a href=\"/Deep_Sjeng\" title=\"Deep Sjeng\">Deep Sjeng</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"DOCCC 2004\"]\n[Site \"Leiden Ned\"]\n[Date \"2004.10.17\"]\n[Round \"06\"]\n[White \"Tao\"]\n[Black \"Deep Sjeng\"]\n[Result \"1/2-1/2\"]\n\n1.c3 e5 2.e4 d5 3.Qa4+ Nd7 4.exd5 Ngf6 5.c4 Bc5 6.Nc3 O-O 7.d3 Nb6 8.Qd1 Qe7 9.Bg5 h6 \n10.Bxf6 Qxf6 11.Nf3 Bd4 12.Be2 Qg6 13.O-O Bh3 14.Ne1 Bd7 15.Nc2 Bh3 16.Bf3 Bxc3 17.bxc3 \nBf5 18.Bh5 Qh7 19.Ne1 e4 20.dxe4 Bxe4 21.Qd4 Rfe8 22.f3 Bf5 23.Rd1 Rad8 24.Rd2 c5 25.Qxc5 \nRc8 26.Qb5 Nxc4 27.Rd4 Ne3 28.Rf2 g6 29.d6 Nd5 30.Rxd5 Rxe1+ 31.Rf1 Rxf1+ 32.Kxf1 Be6 \n33.d7 Rd8 34.Qa5 b6 35.Qxa7 Qg7 36.Qxb6 Qf8 37.Rd4 gxh5 38.a4 Qe7 39.Qc7 Rxd7 40.Rxd7 Bxd7 \n41.c4 Qe6 42.a5 Bc8 43.Qd8+ Kg7 44.Qd4+ Kg6 45.Kf2 Ba6 46.c5 h4 47.Qxh4 Qe2+ 48.Kg3 Qe5+ \n49.Qf4 Qxc5 50.Qe4+ Kg7 51.Qg4+ Kf8 52.Qf4 Qxa5 53.Qxh6+ Kg8 54.h3 Qe5+ 55.f4 Qe1+ 56.Kh2 \nBd3 57.Qg5+ Bg6 58.Qd8+ Kg7 59.Qd4+ Kh7 60.Qc5 Qd2 61.Qe5 Qc2 62.Qf6 Qf2 63.Qe5 Kg8 64.Qg5 \nKg7 65.Qe5+ f6 66.Qe7+ Bf7 67.Qe4 Kh6 68.Qf5 Qb2 69.Qd3 Bg6 70.Qd8 Kg7 71.Qd7+ Bf7 72.Qg4+ \nKh6 73.Qf5 Bc4 74.Qe4 Ba2 75.Qf5 Bb3 76.Kg3 Qd4 77.Kh4 Bf7 78.g3 Bg6 79.Qc8 Kg7 80.Qc1 Bf5 \n81.Qe1 Kf7 82.Qe2 Be6 83.Qh5+ Kf8 84.Qh8+ 1/2-1/2\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Raymond_Smullyan\" title=\"Raymond Smullyan\">Raymond Smullyan</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i>The Tao Is Silent</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HarperCollins\">HarperOne</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Raymond_Smullyan\" title=\"Raymond Smullyan\">Raymond Smullyan</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mit.edu/people/dpolicar/writing/prose/text/godTaoist.html\">Is God a Taoist?</a></i> <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">MIT</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=72400\">Tao</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=134675\">Tao 4.3 (won against Quest, Dutch-ch 2000) is available&#160;!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=147907\">Some questions on Tao</a> by <a href=\"/Peter_Berger\" title=\"Peter Berger\">Peter Berger</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 03, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=149645\">Tao update</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=208102\">Tao at ICC</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=210007\">CCT4 Tao/Quark</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 26, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT4\" title=\"CCT4\">CCT4</a>, <a href=\"/Quark\" title=\"Quark\">Quark</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242621\">About Tao 5.2</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2002</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess\">Chess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-chess.org/doku.php?id=computer_chess:wiki:download:engine_download_list\">Engine Download List</a> from <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski's</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-chess.org/doku.php?id=home\">Computer-Chess Wiki</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=125\">Tao's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/4040/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Tao%205.6#Tao_5_6\">Tao 5.6</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/40</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/kcec/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Tao%205.6\">Tao 5.6</a> in <a href=\"/KCEC\" title=\"KCEC\">KCEC</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tao\">Tao from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tao_%28disambiguation%29\">Tao (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taoism\">Taoism from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yin_and_yang\">Yin and yang from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:The_United_Jazz_%2B_Rock_Ensemble\" title=\"Category:The United Jazz + Rock Ensemble\">The United Jazz + Rock Ensemble</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.allmusic.com/song/yin-mt0012147462\">Yin</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.allmusic.com/album/teamwork-mw0000062413\">Teamwork</a> (1978), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Category:Eberhard_Weber\" title=\"Category:Eberhard Weber\">Eberhard Weber</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Jon_Hiseman\" title=\"Category:Jon Hiseman\">Jon Hiseman</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Barbara_Thompson\" title=\"Category:Barbara Thompson\">Barbara Thompson</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Volker_Kriegel\" title=\"Category:Volker Kriegel\">Volker Kriegel</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Wolfgang_Dauner\" title=\"Category:Wolfgang Dauner\">Wolfgang Dauner</a>,<br /></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Category:Charlie_Mariano\" title=\"Category:Charlie Mariano\">Charlie Mariano</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Albert_Mangelsdorff\" title=\"Category:Albert Mangelsdorff\">Albert Mangelsdorff</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Ian_Carr\" title=\"Category:Ian Carr\">Ian Carr</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ack_van_Rooyen\">Ack van Rooyen</a></dd>\n<dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/HBKN-4bQfVc?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tao&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yin_and_yang\">Yin and yang from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242621\">About Tao 5.2</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessbase.com/newsdetail.asp?newsid=1599\">Shredder and Ruffian lead in Leiden</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a> and <a href=\"/Theo_van_der_Storm\" title=\"Theo van der Storm\">Theo van der Storm</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a>, April 24, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/ICT_2004\" title=\"ICT 2004\">ICT 2004</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=72400\">Tao</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 1999</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=208110\">Re: Tao at ICC</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=149645\">Tao update</a> by <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2001</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\">24th Open Dutch Computer-Chess Championship 2004 Photo Gallery</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301052517\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.076 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.610 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 147/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 330/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4939-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301052516 and revision id 17017\n -->\n"
